@WareHouseInventoryApi_HostAddress = https://localhost:7003

### Get all products (zatiaľ prázdny list)
GET {{WareHouseInventoryApi_HostAddress}}/api/products

### Create a product
POST {{WareHouseInventoryApi_HostAddress}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Kladivo",
  "price": 9.99,
  "stockQuantity": 10
}

### Get by id (po vytvorení)
GET {{WareHouseInventoryApi_HostAddress}}/api/products/1

### Update
PUT {{WareHouseInventoryApi_HostAddress}}/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Kladivo veľké",
  "price": 14.99,
  "stockQuantity": 5
}

### Validácia — negatívna cena (musí dať 400)
POST {{WareHouseInventoryApi_HostAddress}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Skrutka",
  "price": -1,
  "stockQuantity": 100
}

### 404 na neexistujúci id
GET {{WareHouseInventoryApi_HostAddress}}/api/products/9999